{"tid":441963,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"加密唔到","createTime":"2017-10-20T07:22:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T02:45:42.000Z","uid":35418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"0bf34c97b78f7905d38587af69c43aff4302b0cd","tid":441963,"uid":35418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T07:22:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c9dcb92c70f47b88774519430f1e0ab4c077c0f","tid":441963,"uid":1,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T09:02:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"012fdc0a37dc8d609d9cd7ef434dc139c918b7b1","tid":441963,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T09:04:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"175d4d0fcbdb1e7bcb726d6d00538f5baaa8ae11","tid":441963,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T12:21:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">admin可以解釋點解bam濕鳩塞鷗唔bam三色貓未?<br />\n三色貓洗版紀錄</span><br />\n0805 12/10/2017又洗重覆既野<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/oujsx2ya\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Foujsx2ya&h=2d5599af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2000 11/10/2017<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/48neihtl\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F48neihtl&h=9cf086f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n0738 11/8/2017<br />\n又重複post嗰段野洗版<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/m1hkucys\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fm1hkucys&h=3fd5a02a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n三色貓又重覆post呢段野搞事07:25 11/10/2017<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/pc3862hm\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fpc3862hm&h=938f7e35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n多到cap都要cap幾十次<br />\n一日喺時事台開10個8個無關時事既膠post<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/v3le2j4o\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fv3le2j4o&h=e29e1e46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<blockquote>全部post都同時事冇關<br />\n一日可以開幾個洗版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/97uqzyx2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F97uqzyx2&h=0095b1f2&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n更多紀錄<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/avlj83dt\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Favlj83dt&h=f41a0862&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n全部post都同時事冇關<br />\n一日可以開幾個洗版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/97uqzyx2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F97uqzyx2&h=0095b1f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n五毛三色貓46644狂開曹星如膠post引罵戰<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/sufptvbm\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fsufptvbm&h=ef8d0071&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n喺時事台狂開同時事冇關膠post洗版<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/tv12x5yh\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ftv12x5yh&h=3e8803c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/lfnobv4y\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Flfnobv4y&h=6c7fd85f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/focknu9r\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ffocknu9r&h=696519d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/y2kqp4f9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fy2kqp4f9&h=4b9112a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/batnfi4x\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fbatnfi4x&h=97e2d369&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/mn9fgcr7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fmn9fgcr7&h=1a014e97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/twu6yb3o\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ftwu6yb3o&h=ee167fac&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"87084d6824a71e2a4731f6ec43ecb3133c647f5e","tid":441963,"uid":138729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T06:59:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbbdbbf9f94b06cb0a2496cee7958e9fddcc2e9f","tid":441963,"uid":26254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T05:37:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"608e5af86dc18be14d220609c4ecf6c22d52f6a4","tid":441963,"uid":70308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T19:39:05.000Z","msg":"［member] test [/member]"},{"pid":"09cbc42a0a37ee8606a2e7bea51d623bd7d1129c","tid":441963,"uid":70308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T19:39:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47aede69425c8dc8939f2467437b9c99cf74f49f","tid":441963,"uid":70308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T19:40:31.000Z","msg":"[member]點解中文又唔得嘅［/member]"},{"pid":"610f69fac0fff029d9b6bebb7b3ea011b052ccff","tid":441963,"uid":70308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T19:41:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16a391319925cc1401290a17c183867fba415921","ti